snippet.title: Taiwan Love Story ⁵ PV｜Mango Party
snippet.description:
Taiwan Love Story ⁵ is a romantic interactive novel. To write a thesis on love, you meet girls from different parts of Taiwan. As you conduct your academic research, you gradually become captivated by them, leading to a series of sweet, bittersweet, and complex romantic encounters.
#steam #mangoparty #lewdloco
